chapter.sect1:
Upgrading with &susemgr;
&susemgr; is a server solution for providing updates, patches, and security fixes for &sle; clients. It comes with a set of tools and a Web-based user interface for management tasks. See for more information about &susemgr;.
You can perform a system upgrade using &susemgr;. The &ay; technology allows upgrades from one major version to the next.
